snippet.title: Reporting Scammers to POLICE at India's Scam Fort
snippet.description:
Amber Fort in Jaipur is the most beautiful fort in India, but it's infested with scammers. I take you through the fort and report the scams to the Police! But what will the Police do when I complain? We'll find out.

The best part? I ran into two American tourists who watched my videos and thanked me for teaching them the 3 most important words as a foreigner in India "Nahi Chahiye Ji" (I don't want it).

Filmed before Lockdown.
